@startuml Sequence_AsyncPayment
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam maxmessagesize 150
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #2c3e50
    LifeLineBorderColor #34495e
    LifeLineBackgroundColor White
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #ecf0f1
    ParticipantBorderColor #2c3e50
    BoxBackgroundColor #f9f9fa
}

title Fluxo de Pagamento e Emissão de Ingressos (Stripe + BullMQ)

actor Usuário as User
participant "App / Frontend" as Front
box "API Rest (Síncrono)"
    participant "OrdersController" as Controller
    participant "CreateOrder\nUseCase" as CreateOrder
end box
box "Fila (BullMQ)" #e8f4f8
    queue "Redis\n(orders-queue)" as Redis
end box
box "Worker (Assíncrono)"
    participant "OrdersProcessor\n(WorkerHost)" as Worker
    participant "CompleteOrder\nUseCase" as CompleteOrder
    participant "CreateTicket\nUseCase" as CreateTicket
    participant "DispatchTicketEmail\nUseCase" as EmailUseCase
end box
database "PostgreSQL\n(TypeORM)" as DB
participant "Stripe API" as Stripe
participant "Resend API" as Resend

== 1. Iniciando o Pedido de Compra ==
User -> Front: Clicar em "Comprar (Qtd: 2)"
Front -> Controller: POST /orders {ticketTypeId, quantity}
Controller -> CreateOrder: execute(userId, dto)

CreateOrder -> DB: check stock (TicketType)
CreateOrder -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
CreateOrder -> DB: update available_quantity (decrement)
CreateOrder -> DB: insert Order (status: PENDING)

CreateOrder -> Stripe: createCheckoutSession(orderId, price, quantity)
Stripe --> CreateOrder: sessionUrl, sessionId

CreateOrder -> DB: update session_id on Order
CreateOrder -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION

CreateOrder --> Controller: { orderId, checkoutUrl }
Controller --> Front: HTTP 201 Created (Redirect URL)
Front -> Stripe: Redireciona usuário para Checkout Stripe

== 2. Pagamento e Webhook (Assíncrono) ==
note over Stripe: Usuário paga com Cartão
Stripe -> Controller: POST /orders/webhook (checkout.session.completed)
note over Controller: Valida header stripe-signature

Controller -> Redis: BullMQ.add('complete-order-job', { orderId })
Redis --> Controller: job added
Controller --> Stripe: HTTP 200 OK (received: true)

== 3. Processamento do Pedido ==
Redis -[#blue]-> Worker: process(job)
Worker -> CompleteOrder: execute(orderId)

CompleteOrder -> DB: findOrder(orderId)
DB --> CompleteOrder: order (status: PENDING, quantity: 2)
CompleteOrder -> DB: updateOrder(orderId, status: PAID)

loop para cada ingresso (Ex: 2 vezes)
    CompleteOrder -> CreateTicket: execute(dto, userId)
    CreateTicket -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    CreateTicket -> CreateTicket: generateTicketToken() (QR Code JWT)
    CreateTicket -> DB: insert Ticket (status: VALID, qrCode)
    CreateTicket -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION
    CreateTicket --> CompleteOrder: TicketResponseDto
    
    note over CreateTicket, EmailUseCase: Fire and Forget (sem await)
    CreateTicket -> EmailUseCase: execute(ticketId, token) (Assíncrono)
end

CompleteOrder --> Worker: finalizado
Worker --> Redis: job concluído

== 4. Disparo do E-mail ==
EmailUseCase -> DB: find Ticket & User relations
DB --> EmailUseCase: Ticket data (email, event title)
EmailUseCase -> EmailUseCase: GenerateQrCodeImage (Buffer)
EmailUseCase -> Resend: sendTicketEmail(email, QRCode)
Resend --> EmailUseCase: accepted
@enduml